socialData.name: Brent Arveseth
socialData.title: Commercial Business Development Officer
socialData.bio: I was thrown into finding solutions for companies and people over 10 years ago.....I was given a phone, some contacts and was told to get to get people involved. I did just that. I haven't looked back since. My goal is to give 100% to each and every client. To help each client individually reach their goals. Building a relationship of trust and integrity. Each client is given the same attention, respect and can expect I do exactly what I say I will do. I pride myself on streamlining the process from start to finish. I am not afraid to ask questions and to maneuver options to enhance customer satisfaction and finish the job, all while keeping high energy and client satisfaction the top priority. This experience has provided opportunity to make significant contributions in each assignment I have completed. Consistently, I have brought about new ideas, ways of thinking, problem-solving skills that have produced results. I am versatile, possess leadership strategies, and have gained the respect of those with whom I have come in contact. I offer a high degree of integrity, and I believe my strong sense of career commitment would be an asset in any business services. Specialties: Appraisals, Compliance, TRID, Mortgages (FHA, USDA, VA, Jumbo) Marketing, Client Relations
